Description: Naruto’s friends are threatened, the mysteries of Pain deepen and Naruto must fight to protect his village.
Title: NARUTO 46
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. How is a human teenager to survive?
Title: ROSARIO   VAMPIRE, VOL. 9
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 3
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: The detective known as L is scheduled to die in 23 days. That leaves him with 22 days to stop a terrorist group from unleashing a virus upon the world.
Title: DEATH NOTE: L, CHANGE THE WORLD
Author: M

Description: Yugi, the king of games, must face off against Yako Tenma, the protege of a Maxmilion Pegasus, who Yugi had previously vanquished.
Title: YU-GI-OH! R, VOL. 1
Author: Kazuki Takahashi and Akira Ito
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi and Akira Ito

Description: Two brothers harmed in a ritual that was half magic/half science seek the legendary Philosopher’s Stone to make things right. But others seek the weapon of alchemy for their own nefarious means.
Title: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST, VOL. 20
Author: Hiromu Arakawa

Description: Karin, a vampire who every month bleeds profusely from her nose, is kidnapped by a gang of vampires who want to use her blood for their own survival.
Title: CHIBI VAMPIRE, VOL. 14
Author: Yuna Kagesaki

Description: The romance between Raven, a goth girl, and Alexander, a vampire, continues to be plagued by Alexander’s cousin, Claude, who is half-human and half-vampire.
Title: VAMPIRE KISSES VOL. 3, BLOOD RELATIVES
Author: Ellen Schreiber, Elisa Kwon and  Rem
Contributor: by Ellen Schreiber, Elisa Kwon and  Rem

Description: Haine, who was given away to another family as part of a business loan, reunites with her blood relatives. Meanwhile, the twins Shizumasa and Takanari fight over their love for her.
Title: THE GENTLEMEN’S ALLIANCE, VOL. 10
Author: Arina Tanemura

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 28
Author: Tite Kubo
